First Department,

March, 1964*

(March 19, 1964) Hyman D. Siegel v. The People of the State of New York.

Not published with other decisions of March 19, 1964, 20 A D 2d 771. — [Rep.

Motion for an order pursuant to CPLR (5704, subd. [a]) vacating any order of the Supreme Court of the State of New York, County of New York, and for other relief denied. Concur—Breitel, J. P., Valente, McNally and Eager, JJ.
